body_html:
Thanks for the contribution! We'd prefer not to commit language bindings to the tensorflow repository that the core TensorFlow team won't yet maintain.

I'm happy to do code review on the Swift bindings and link to them on tensorflow.org when they're functional, though.

body:
Thanks for the contribution! We'd prefer not to commit language bindings to the tensorflow repository that the core TensorFlow team won't yet maintain.

I'm happy to do code review on the Swift bindings and link to them on `tensorflow.org` when they're functional, though.
